   MISCOMP Electronic Requisitioning MISER

   Welcome to the MISCOMP Electronic Requisitioning (MISER) home page.

   From here, Computing Division personnel may submit purchase
   requisitions and follow their status using the query options.

   You must have a MISER username and password to create, view, copy or
   perform any other activity on a purchase request. You may use the
   MISCOMP User Access page to request access or change your password.

