   Update, Copy, Query or Print an Existing Purchase Request (?)

   Perform one of the following options on
   Request Number ____________________ (CD Number)

   Edit View Clone Cancel Renew Blanket Expire Blanket Issue Change Order

   Print [Choose Printer] Or Enter Print Queue: ____________________
   View Printout

   Or, use the MISER Purchase Request Query Page to query requests one a
   wider basis. For example, you can query all your requests that are
   currently in Purchasing.
